OL,3,CBirmingham City chairman Tom Wagner in
OL,4,Crecovery after suffering stroke
OL,6,FBirmingham City chairman Tom Wagner is
OL,7,Fin recovery after suffering a stroke.
OL,9,FThe football club confirmed that Mr
OL,10,FWagner is making 'good' progress after
OL,11,Frapid medical intervention.
OL,13,FThe 56-year-old will step back from
OL,14,Fday-to-day activity for a period of
OL,15,Ftime to focus on his health.
OL,17,FHowever, the club wrote, Mr Wanger
OL,18,Fremains closely connected to the club,
OL,19,Fand they look forward to welcoming him
OL,20,Fback.
