OL,3,CBirmingham City chairman Tom Wagner in
OL,4,Crecovery after suffering stroke
OL,6,F"Thanks to rapid medical intervention,
OL,7,Fhe received immediate treatment and is
OL,8,Fnow receiving excellent care. We are
OL,9,Fpleased to share that he is making a
OL,10,Fgood recovery.
OL,12,F"While he will be stepping back from
OL,13,Fday-to-day activity for a period of
OL,14,Ftime to focus on his recovery, Tom
OL,15,Fremains closely connected to the club,
OL,16,Fand we all look forward to welcoming
OL,17,Fhim back.
