OL,3,CBirmingham City chairman Tom Wagner in
OL,4,Crecovery after suffering stroke
OL,6,F"Birmingham City Football Club is
OL,7,Fincredibly important to Tom and to the
OL,8,Fentire Knighthead team. Their
OL,9,Fcommitment to the club is unchanged,
OL,10,Fand our plans and operations continue
OL,11,Fas normal under strong leadership.
OL,13,F"We appreciate your continued support
OL,14,Fand ask that you respect Tom's privacy
OL,15,Fduring his recovery.
OL,17,FThank you, as always, for standing
OL,18,Fbehind the Blues. Keep Right On."
